commit.title: Windows packaging build with Gitlab CI
commit.message:
Windows packaging build with Gitlab CI

We use a specific runner on an Inria CloudStack, to make it possible to
automatically generate signed Windows packages (for protected branches,
PRs will generate unsigned packages once we set up the Gitlab fork for
PR mirroring).
